    • Enum Constant Detail

      • NETWORKED_CLIENT

        public static final UrlyBirdApplicationMode NETWORKED_CLIENT
        Network mode; only display the suncertify.gui.client.URLyBirdClientGui and use network access.

        This is the default application mode; to run the application in this mode the user will not specify any Command Line Arguments.

      • STANDALONE_CLIENT

        public static final UrlyBirdApplicationMode STANDALONE_CLIENT
        Standalone mode; only display the suncertify.gui.client.URLyBirdClientGui and not use network access.
